Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.16,0:00:04.66,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,When watching TV,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.66,0:00:06.14,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,please keep the room bright...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.14,0:00:08.27,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,...and sit well away from the TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.27,0:00:09.19,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.54,0:00:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you are, Mistress \NKuzuha. Please say, "Ah!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.83,0:00:24.83,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Butler Economy, Trade and Industry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.88,0:00:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The futures index of the butlers \Nat our Hakuou Academy is...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.83,0:00:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Down 3 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.95,0:00:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They have grown soft.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.18,0:00:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A butler, for example, can get run over \Nby a car speeding along at 80kmph
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.74,0:00:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or get trampled by a giant robot...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.30,0:00:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon. A bit of cream on your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.45,0:00:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only when they can survive such \Nthings as if it were nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.77,0:00:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,can they be considered full-fledged butlers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.04,0:00:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I not right, Sion?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.69,0:00:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.55,0:00:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.37,0:00:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me think...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.71,0:00:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there were a butler somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.05,0:00:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with a look of poverty about him \Nthat just makes you want to smack him,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.64,0:01:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who was in his late teens \Nand roughly 168cm and 57kg...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.37,0:01:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there were?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.98,0:01:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I would not be against \Ngiving him some special attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.69,0:01:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure is autumn.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.23,0:01:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It certainly is autumn.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.00,0:01:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tama, cut it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.60,0:01:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, cut it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.80,0:01:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rarrr!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.14,0:01:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rarrr!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.32,0:01:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rarrr...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.12,0:01:36.89,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.89,0:01:39.87,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I feel like someone \Nis calling to me from somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.27,0:01:43.62,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's about time we busted out a new.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.62,0:01:46.80,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Whosoever commands the butlers, \Ncommands the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.80,0:01:52.29,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,The Great Butler War that will \Nshake up the world has just begun!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.33,0:01:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know! I have just thought \Nof a good way to stave off boredom!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.52,0:01:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, so uh... Who might you be?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.18,0:02:01.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Zettai nante shinjinai!\NI don't believe in absolutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.05,0:02:04.72,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukanou nante nai!\NNo such thing as impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.89,0:02:10.02,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Mirai wa hiraku te no naka ni aru\NThe future is in the open palm of my hands
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.19,0:02:15.23,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Dou yattemo katenai akuma ga\NA demon that I just can't win against
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.53,0:02:20.32,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Megami no kao o shite chakkari (O_O;)\NBrazenly pretending to be a goddess (O_O;)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.03,0:02:25.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Keikenchi ja tannai kurai dakara\NExperience points are almost not enough
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.37,0:02:31.79,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Isshou tanren shikou-sakugo ni sessa-takuma\NTraining for life, working hard at trial and error
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.25,0:02:36.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Mondai nara muzukashii-hodo ude ga naru shi\NTougher the problem the more it gets me going
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.30,0:02:41.47,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Yorokobu kao ga mirerya sore de ii shi\NSeeing the joy on your face is enough for me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.55,0:02:47.31,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Takara no chizu o boku wa te ni ireta\NI've found a treasure map
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.18,0:02:53.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Juuou-mujin kimi o tsurete tsuki-susumou!\NTotally free, I'll take you and push forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.98,0:02:56.57,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Happii na kanchigai\NA happy misunderstanding
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.57,0:02:59.20,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Chikai wa yuruganai!\NMy pledge will stand fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.45,0:03:04.41,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaze no yukue mo kaete-miseru\NI'll even change the direction of the wind
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.91,0:03:07.41,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakkou wa kini-shinai\NI won't care how I look
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.41,0:03:10.25,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Unmei ja kujikenai!\NNo destiny will discourage me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.46,0:03:15.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Ano kumo chirasu hayate no gotoku!\NLike the sudden gale scattering the clouds!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.65,0:03:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate Rising
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.61,0:03:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've done it! It's finally complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.29,0:03:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.98,0:03:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll win the new author \Naward for sure this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.94,0:03:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.02,0:03:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Then make sure to get this manuscript...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.61,0:03:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I will send it out to the publisher.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.08,0:03:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, also...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.20,0:03:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you go to school, grab the PSP \Nfrom my desk while you're at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.25,0:03:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, did you forget it there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.32,0:04:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's got Crisis Core in it. I'm working \Non finishing a hardcore challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.80,0:04:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.76,0:04:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.88,0:04:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, please get some good rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.46,0:04:16.60,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,A normal, peaceful morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.85,0:04:20.99,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a bit disappointing that \Nthe Miss couldn't make it, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.99,0:04:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Hayate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.82,0:04:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Hinagiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.68,0:04:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alone? Is Nagi playing hooky again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.31,0:04:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.17,0:04:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, students of Hakuou Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.46,0:04:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is early, but I have some \Ninteresting information for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.68,0:04:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This voice is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.81,0:04:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Look, Hinagiku!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.48,0:04:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will have you know, this is no joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.98,0:04:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.11,0:04:49.93,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.48,0:04:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That woman's up to no good again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.94,0:04:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.32,0:05:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.03,0:05:12.29,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,elzzaD
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.30,0:05:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"D-Dazzle! The First..."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.29,0:05:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Hakuou Academy..."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.54,0:05:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"B-Butler..."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.29,0:05:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Battle..."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.21,0:05:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Tournament..."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.78,0:05:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hinagiku, um, please calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.52,0:05:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world is this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.12,0:05:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate, you stay back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.27,0:05:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh-ho, I am surprised \Nyou knew where to find me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.02,0:05:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are not our student body \Npresident for nothing, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.56,0:05:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, who is this woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.75,0:05:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's our school's Superintendent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.67,0:05:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Superintendent?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.92,0:05:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.53,0:05:52.70,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Hakuou Academy Butler \NBattle Tournament to be Held!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.54,0:05:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.06,0:05:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Butler Battle Tournament?! \NYou're making no sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.82,0:05:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's exactly what it sounds like.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.50,0:05:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to check up on the level \Nof the butlers at our school.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.61,0:06:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I also have a somewhat \Npersonal interest in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.00,0:06:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A strong, tough butler worthy \Nof some special attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.89,0:06:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is what I am looking for!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.96,0:06:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That gave me the chills \Nfor some reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.28,0:06:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she seems like an awfully \Nextreme sort of person.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.39,0:06:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-In other words, \Nyou're up to your usual thing
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.59,0:06:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you plan to have fun by treating \Nthe students as your toys, don't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.07,0:06:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Have fun"?! How insulting!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.07,0:06:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ability to fight is one of the most \Nimportant aspects of being a butler!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.99,0:06:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But all the butlers \Nat this school are serious students!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.14,0:06:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For example, take Hayate here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.74,0:06:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.78,0:06:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, then perhaps \NI shall ask him directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.21,0:06:45.92,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait, have I been made \Nthe focus of this conversation
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.92,0:06:48.61,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,before I could even understand \Nwhat's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.61,0:06:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.93,0:06:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the looks of it, you seem to be \Nat least some sort of butler yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.63,0:06:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer my question.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.45,0:06:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.31,0:06:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A battle tournament such as this
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.94,0:07:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"to test the strength \Nof butlers is pointless."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.95,0:07:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now... "Yes" or "no"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.60,0:07:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.51,0:07:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beep. Beep. Beep.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.19,0:07:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, I wouldn't say \Nthat it was pointless,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.95,0:07:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,b-but I think there might be \Nmore important things than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.12,0:07:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like one's dedication to one's mistress...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.62,0:07:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.80,0:07:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.30,0:07:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You understand nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.75,0:07:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate, take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.94,0:07:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to have {\i1}some{\i0} skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.77,0:07:34.87,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on! Please don't just drag me \Ninto your battle world!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.20,0:07:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But at this rate, you \Nstill have a long way to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.39,0:07:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What should I do? This is my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.88,0:07:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A butler is tasked with \Nthe protection of his mistress,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.90,0:07:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even if it should cost him his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.59,0:08:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy, what would you do \Nif I were out to kill your mistress?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.77,0:08:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you still be able to \Nsay the same thing then?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.22,0:08:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That strength is not a particularly \Nessential quality for a butler...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.57,0:08:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.05,0:08:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You left yourself open!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.66,0:08:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A lesson for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.81,0:08:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.03,0:08:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.01,0:08:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She ran out of juice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.90,0:08:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not good... My blood sugar level...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.61,0:08:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sion... a sna... a snack...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.01,0:08:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I already have one waiting \Nfor you in your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.50,0:08:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it sweet?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.06,0:08:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, very.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.55,0:08:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sion...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.85,0:08:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mistress Kuzuha...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.60,0:08:48.42,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh, my!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.78,0:08:51.84,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world is up with these people?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.84,0:08:53.14,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.14,0:08:55.90,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Hakuou Academy Superintendent, \NKirika Kuzuha,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.90,0:08:58.08,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,has triple the combat \Nability of a normal person,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.08,0:09:00.54,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,but in exchange, if she uses up her energy,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.54,0:09:04.30,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,she just drops like a fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.47,0:09:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you do that \Nto my precious Mistress Kuzuha...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.42,0:09:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't get away with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.23,0:09:14.52,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what? I'm going to \Nbe held solely responsible for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.20,0:09:22.11,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.11,0:09:25.08,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Could this be the Territory \Nformed by this person's Aura?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.51,0:09:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Sion.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.46,0:09:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Written as "si" as in "poet" \Nand "on" as in "sound".
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.20,0:09:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sion.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.55,0:09:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh, is that so? I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.36,0:09:39.80,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,This person is good!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.80,0:09:42.05,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been robbed of my \Nfreedom before I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.05,0:09:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a butler? What \Nis this world coming to?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.54,0:09:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you are so weak...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.07,0:09:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you just give up being a butler
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.96,0:09:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and switch to being a maid?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.33,0:09:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That would suit you better.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.89,0:10:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that makes you angry, \Ntry entering the Tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.52,0:10:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The winner will receive \Nthe privilege of challenging me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.91,0:10:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though, I doubt you could ever manage that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.30,0:10:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, um, Hayate, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.00,0:10:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For, you know, getting you mixed up in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.22,0:10:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.96,0:10:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.01,0:10:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please pretend you didn't \Nsee that... just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.44,0:10:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.75,0:10:38.15,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Where's all this leading to?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.15,0:10:40.84,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world is this \NButler Battle Tournament?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.47,0:10:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I'd like to ask you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.79,0:10:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,J-Just what kind of person \Nis the Superintendent of Hakuou Academy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.06,0:10:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And she seems to have some \Nsort of history with Hinagiku...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.99,0:10:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, did you run into her today?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.19,0:10:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.38,0:10:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that Superintendent's \Na fantastically troublesome character.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.27,0:11:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For example, just to stave off boredom,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.35,0:11:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she changed our field trip destination
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.50,0:11:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to the non-Internet Amazon \Nwithout our consent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.11,0:11:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.84,0:11:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or simply to stave off boredom,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.98,0:11:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she schemed to open \Na pool made solely for Char.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.53,0:11:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.07,0:11:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, it's kind of been like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.45,0:11:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with Hinagiku trying \Nto protect the students and Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.45,0:11:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from the evil reach \Nof the Superintendent's whims.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.53,0:11:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hold on...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.03,0:11:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, that last part...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.75,0:11:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, here's a bit of friendly advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.66,0:11:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Better not get involved \Nwith that Superintendent or her butler.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.46,0:11:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this Butler Battle Tournament \Nsure came out of the blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.96,0:11:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.26,0:11:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The winner will be presented \Nwith a prize of 100 school credits."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.73,0:11:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's like a roundabout way of saying \Nyou can skip all the classes you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.98,0:11:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate, if you don't mind, \Nwhy don't you enter this tournament?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.84,0:11:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.68,0:11:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... Miss, you don't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.23,0:11:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, I don't care about the 100 credits.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.47,0:12:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether it's there or not, \NI'll skip school when I skip school.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.53,0:12:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.46,0:12:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.90,0:12:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate, I wish to see it for myself \Nwith these very eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.61,0:12:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when you win the tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.67,0:12:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Win, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.75,0:12:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.70,0:12:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, you must be invincible \Nto be a Sanzenin butler.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.86,0:12:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.09,0:12:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...invincible!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.13,0:12:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Invincible!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.30,0:12:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which equates to victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.59,0:12:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.97,0:12:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh! I'm starting to get more \Nand more excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.73,0:12:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because knowing you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.37,0:12:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Things like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.41,0:12:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and this...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.13,0:12:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...should be in your arsenal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.99,0:12:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's not often I get to \Nsee stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.31,0:12:43.38,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... So, with the way this is going,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.38,0:12:46.16,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,am I pretty much being forced \Nto enter the tournament, no matter what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.61,0:12:50.79,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,But if the Miss has such \Nhigh expectations of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.42,0:12:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hinagiku Katsura, this is a warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.76,0:13:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ultimately, you are \Na commoner without a butler.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.82,0:13:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be for your own good \Nto mind your own business
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.56,0:13:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and refrain from interfering \Nwith the Tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.72,0:13:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I retrieved this tape earlier \Nfrom the student council post box.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.44,0:13:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Incidentally, the packaging was all sticky \Nwith brown sugar syrup.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.98,0:13:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, so her snack today consisted \Nof Japanese sweets (wagashi).
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.44,0:13:21.40,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,My Master (wagashi)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.19,0:13:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,None of that matters!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.88,0:13:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't there some way for us \Nto intervene in this Tournament?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.69,0:13:33.12,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Having said that, I have no butler...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.12,0:13:35.12,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what am I going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.12,0:13:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've made up my mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.07,0:13:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to ask Kotetsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.88,0:13:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be nice \Nfor those of you with butlers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.69,0:13:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The 100 credits are definitely appealing,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.75,0:13:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but now, what are Miki and I to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.27,0:13:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, there! Don't be letting \Nthe devil's temptation get to you already!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.78,0:13:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mm-hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.08,0:13:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hina, I have a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.32,0:14:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, perhaps you should refrain \Nfrom anything so dangerous?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.11,0:14:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I've made up my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.05,0:14:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maria, I'm going to enter \Nthe Butler Battle Tournament!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.13,0:14:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot let the Miss down!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.92,0:14:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! I'm starting to get more \Nand more fired up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.19,0:14:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will try going with the \Nflow, in spite of it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.33,0:14:22.67,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Even with this hot-blooded turn of events,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.67,0:14:25.01,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess he's still off in his own world.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.01,0:14:26.68,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,What of butler Hayate's fate?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.68,0:14:32.22,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And... the day of the Tournament's \Ncome around in no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.34,0:14:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A warrior is as good as his word. \N({\i1}Bu{\i0}shi ni nigon wa na{\i1}i{\i0}.)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.58,0:14:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Die once and you cannot die again. \N({\i1}I{\i0}chido shineba nido shina{\i1}nu{\i0}.)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.04,0:14:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are they burning it up over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.73,0:14:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now, we hereby commence Dazzle!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.35,0:14:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The First Hakuou Academy \NButler Battle Tournament!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.18,0:15:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the Superintendent \Nof this academy, Kirika Kuzuha!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.04,0:15:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of you, vie against one another!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.67,0:15:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Compete ruthlessly!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.28,0:15:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I expect tough fights worthy \Nof this great stage for butlers!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.51,0:15:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's finally time, Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.29,0:15:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.61,0:15:20.69,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait for me, poem person!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.96,0:15:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now, we'll begin the first match!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.72,0:15:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the red corner, the butler \Nof some household, Other 1!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.41,0:15:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And in the blue corner, butler of \Nthe Segawa household, Kotetsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.65,0:15:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never knew the committee \Nchairman had a butler.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.08,0:15:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But no one's coming out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.68,0:15:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After I begged him to come, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.72,0:15:56.47,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!! Urakari Main Line
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.50,0:15:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Farewell, Urakari Main Line!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.64,0:16:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This roundish shape of the \Ntrain carriage is just to die for!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.40,0:16:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?! Right, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.98,0:16:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Red corner wins by default!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.92,0:16:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.73,0:16:13.43,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Next up, the second match.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.02,0:16:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, Ayasaki! So yer in this, too, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.66,0:16:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-One of the members of the \N"very generous people" folk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.45,0:16:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How in the world?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.01,0:16:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hired him as an interim butler.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.53,0:16:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Miss Asakaze!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.25,0:16:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost at rock-paper-scissors to Miki, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.07,0:16:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I used my connections to get a pinch hitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.78,0:16:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of connections do you have?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.38,0:16:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rock-paper-scissors?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.60,0:16:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.88,0:16:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.31,0:16:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beat him to a pulp!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.33,0:16:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stick it to him good!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.00,0:16:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.28,0:16:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You win!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.88,0:17:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, please, just don't \Ntell anyone about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.27,0:17:01.90,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.90,0:17:04.71,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,A butler's necktie is his soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.71,0:17:07.21,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Regardless of the amount of damage \Nor if there is even any damage,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.21,0:17:10.09,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,the butler whose necktie \Ngets taken first loses.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.75,0:17:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The winner is Kashiwagi, \Nbutler of the Asakaze household!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.32,0:17:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh, right, his name is Mr. Kashiwagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.45,0:17:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.26,0:17:22.99,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Kashiwagi! Kashiwagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.08,0:17:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.30,0:17:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it up and get me those 100 credits.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.48,0:17:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be sure to do the work \NI've been paid to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.23,0:17:31.65,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Heh Heh Heh
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.63,0:17:31.65,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,S-So black... There's something \Nso black about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.13,0:17:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next up, the third match!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.17,0:17:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the red corner, butler of the Azumamiya \Nhousehold, Kaede Nonohara!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.91,0:17:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nonohara, go for the win!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.64,0:17:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get the 100 credits!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.82,0:17:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.13,0:17:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nonohara...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.36,0:17:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And... his opponent is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.95,0:17:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.69,0:18:07.05,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Power of Flower
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.05,0:18:11.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And someday, even that bud
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.81,0:18:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.60,0:18:17.70,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Will bloom large right \Nin the middle of your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.15,0:18:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Interim butler of the Hanabishi \Nhousehold, Hinagiku Katsura!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.67,0:18:23.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Power of Flower
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.95,0:18:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why is Hinagiku...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.11,0:18:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a-a butler?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.03,0:18:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is because I won against \NRisa at rock-paper-scissors
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.34,0:18:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I gained the draft rights.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.59,0:18:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hina wants to upset \Nthe Superintendent's plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.96,0:18:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want the 100 credits.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.37,0:18:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's a so-called \Naligning of interests.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.27,0:18:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this, victory is ours!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.36,0:18:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good grief, an interim butler, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.71,0:18:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People seem to have a lot of contempt \Nfor our profession these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.27,0:18:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I've offended you, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.24,0:18:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But by no means did I enter \Nthis Tournament as a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.99,0:18:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, shall we begin?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.44,0:19:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.32,0:19:03.78,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.80,0:19:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh-ho. You're pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.60,0:19:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nonohara, you seem awfully sure of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.39,0:19:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why haven't you tried \Nto use your super lethal technique?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.81,0:19:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.48,0:19:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nonohara, go for the win! \NGet the 100 credits!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.86,0:19:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't hit Miss Katsura!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.77,0:19:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how powerful your technique is,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.08,0:19:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Hinagiku Katsura, will repel all \Nyour attacks with everything I have!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.02,0:19:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.63,0:19:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then here I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.19,0:19:57.30,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Safety Shutter!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.34,0:19:56.59,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\pos(320,264)}Safety Shutter\N Super Explosive Flaming Slash of Darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.20,0:20:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I will not be beat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.41,0:20:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? Is that all you've got?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.69,0:20:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Safety...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.48,0:20:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nonohara, the build-up to your \Ntechnique takes a bit too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.06,0:20:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I win.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.95,0:20:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The winner is Hinagiku Katsura!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.67,0:20:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.99,0:20:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For not going easy on me, \Njust because I'm a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.63,0:20:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A butler fights with everything he has, \Nno matter the opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.43,0:20:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.96,0:20:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even my master does not wish \Nfor me to win against you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.65,0:20:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nonohara...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.60,0:20:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you like that?! \NI'm one step closer to you two now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.03,0:20:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.17,0:21:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.40,0:21:02.78,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Hinagiku...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.55,0:21:06.81,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And finally, it was Hayate's turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.92,0:21:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, next match!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.79,0:21:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the red corner, butler of the \NSanzenin household, Hayate Ayasaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.96,0:21:15.59,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.59,0:21:17.96,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, who will be my opponent?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.58,0:21:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the blue corner! Who the heck \Nis it under that mask?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.93,0:21:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mystery butler!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.34,0:21:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Free-style K!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.81,0:21:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who could that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.41,0:21:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That air of dignity could only be \Nthat of a true master.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.91,0:21:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. And he's even got \Na strange tiger with him, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.35,0:21:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who in the world is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.02,0:21:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.25,0:21:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't let your guard down, Hayate.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.98,0:21:47.05,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Who might this mystery butler and tiger be?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.05,0:21:51.28,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, he will fight against \Na critically desperate situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.95,0:21:53.95,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Waratte lun-lun-lun\NSmile lun-lun-lun
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.95,0:21:57.75,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Lala-lun-lun-lulu naita hi mo\NLala-lun-lun-lulu even on a day I've cried
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.75,0:22:03.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Sawagu kaze ni yureru egao kokoro hareteku\NA smile wavers in the wind and clears my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.42,0:22:06.67,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyou mo lun-lun-lun mawarun-lun-lulu\NToday again lun-lun-lun turning lun-lun-lulu
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.67,0:22:17.89,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiyou no shita de kimi to odoru kimagure na dansu\NA whimsical dance with you under the sun
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.31,0:22:25.90,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanige-naku sashi-dasu te ni mitorete\NRiveted by the hand you've casually offered
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.19,0:22:32.49,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsugi no kotoba maigo ni natchau no\NMy next words become lost
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.49,0:22:37.46,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Otonabite tsutsumi-komu manazashi ni\NThe mature gaze that envelopes me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.66,0:22:42.46,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuyogari wasurete-yuku\NMakes me forget my bravado
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.04,0:22:49.13,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Sotto furetete nemurenai yoru no nagai toki mo\NKeep that soft touch on long sleepless nights
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.30,0:22:54.35,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Yume kara sameta bakari no hoho ni mo\NAnd on my cheek, just awakened from a dream
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.14,0:22:56.10,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Lun-lun-lun\NLun-lun-lun
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.10,0:22:59.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Lala-lun-lun-lulu tsun to shita\NLala-lun-lun-lulu that hoity profile
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.44,0:23:05.61,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Yokogao hora atto iu ma waratteru desho?\NLook, there's a smile there already, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.61,0:23:08.82,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora to lun-lun-lun mawarun-lun-lulu\NWith the sky lun-lun-lun turning lun-lun-lulu
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.82,0:23:13.28,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Kimi ga fukasu kaze no naka\NIn a breeze of your making
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.28,0:23:20.16,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Odoru hidamari no dansu\NA dance in a sunny spot
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.79,0:23:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Nagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.75,0:23:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and Hayate's...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.71,0:23:29.55,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sign: Butler Report
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.71,0:23:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Butler Report!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.06,0:23:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G'morn! I'm Nagi Sanzenin.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.09,0:23:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Hayate Ayasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.22,0:23:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With a new warning, opening, \Nand ending, it's a fresh start.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.71,0:23:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it is, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.85,0:23:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like we can fight \Nfor another half a year with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.02,0:23:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had all kinds of worries, but I guess \Nthings have a way of working out.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.52,0:23:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not entirely true. This show has \Na lot of people keeping an eye on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.90,0:23:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About the new opening song \Nwe have starting today...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.09,0:23:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's on a grand scale that makes \Nyou think of the universe, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.57,0:23:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.60,0:23:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though, of course, \Nit's still quite a nice song.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.87,0:23:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Buh-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.74,0:23:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,224)}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.30,0:24:00.82,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's been many months since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.74,0:24:16.14,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\pos(174,307)}The next episode of \N"Hayate the Combat Butler" is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.82,0:24:04.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate, you're always doing your best \Nand I'm grateful to you for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.40,0:24:05.36,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.36,0:24:09.63,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Hakuou Academy Butler Battle Tournament \Nfinally gets to the championship round.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.63,0:24:14.22,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Will Hayate Ayasaki manage \Nto remain a contender?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.22,0:24:17.26,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,There is something \NI absolutely must protect!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.26,0:24:18.28,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.64,0:24:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Hayate the Combat Butler \NBlack Hayate
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.28,0:24:19.95,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on "Hayate the Combat Butler",
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.95,0:24:21.10,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Black Hayate".
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.10,0:24:23.01,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,At crosswalks, even \Nwhen you have a green light,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.01,0:24:25.18,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,make sure you look around \Nand cross carefully!
